{
  "stem": "10699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I saw-- when the mother couldn't stand the appel for so many hours, when they collapsed and the kapo went and started to beat them up, I said, would I have been able to take that, that a kapo or a guard, a German guard, should go and beat my mother up, and I can't do anything about it?",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How would I be able to take that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were sent right away the next day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think I was in a terrible state because I think I wasn't normal for a few days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a shock.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I was under-- in shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were sent-- we were sent to-- near the railways to make trenches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we saw arriving the ghetto from Litzmannstadt, the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And these people, you could see that they had gone through hell already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were already skin, skin and bones, badly dressed, in a terrible way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked them where they were coming from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said they hadn't noticed that we were working there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I asked them where they're coming from.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they told us they came from Litzmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Nobody came in of these people, nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just passed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed into the camp, of that convoy anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Crematorium.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, what we noticed very soon, we were-- we were doing trenches and trenches and trenches.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we, we didn't know why we were doing these trenches, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we soon understood because we were somehow-- our block was facing the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we saw fire-- and the smell, and the-- the terrible smell in the camp, and the flames.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
